        <li>• <strong>Consistency:</strong> Reliable alpha wave activation every time</li>
        <li>• <strong>Convenience:</strong> 11-minute sessions that fit into any schedule</li>
        <li>• <strong>Measurable progress:</strong> Track improvements over time</li>
        <li>• <strong>Professional quality:</strong> Scientifically-tuned frequencies</li>
      </ul>
      
