          size="lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Increasing alpha brainwaves naturally is definitely possible through meditation, 
      breathing exercises, nature exposure, proper nutrition, and quality sleep. These 
